snippet.textDisplay: That last time we met, as soon as i play this song those exact moments flashes in front of me. That hour when it was finally done and dusted and we realised how we are suffering. She cried and looking at her tears,I couldn’t hold anymore. I can never ever forget. She asked, ofc you’re gonna find someone and move on, this too will pass. And i said that i could never love anyone like her anymore. Cut to 3 months and still not a single day passes where there are not memories of her. I have a girl who treats me better than anything but still that Rahil is not there anymore. Love is really strange indeed. You fall for the person you know is not right for you. “That ja raha hoon mai, ja rahi hu mai” couldn’t be better understood than me and couldn’t be better represented than this song.
